title: Finding the edges of jamstack
heroTitle: Finding The Edges of the JAMstack with Tara Z. Manicsic

heroDescription.heroDescription: Curious about what Jamstack can and can’t do? Join Tara from Netlify and Sam from Auth0 as they take a look at what Jamstack is great for, what it’s not so great for, and what the future holds.

childMarkdownRemark.rawMarkdownBody: Curious about what Jamstack can and can’t do? Join Tara from Netlify and Sam from Auth0 as they take a look at what Jamstack is great for, what it’s not so great for, and what the future holds.

subModules.title: Finding The Edges of the JAMstack

intro.intro: Tara Z. Manicsic is a lifelong student, teacher, and maker. She has spent her career using JavaScript on both back-end and front-end to create applications. A Developer Experience Engineer for Netlify, Google Developer Expert, and international technical speaker, she focuses on conveying the codebase she has learned.
